  {% endcodeblock %}

Image tag

Syntax:
  {% img [class names] /path/to/image [width] [height] [title text [alt text]] %}

Include code tag

Syntax:
  {% include_code [title] [lang:language] path/to/file %}

Link tag

Syntax:
  {% link text url [external] [title] %}

Pullquote tag

Syntax:
  {% pullquote [class] %}
  Quote string
  {% endpullquote %}

Raw tag

Syntax:
  {% rawblock %}
  Unescaped string
  {% endrawblock %}

